@startuml ContentManagement
left to right direction

actor "Instructor" as instructor
actor "System (S3)" as s3_system
actor "Student" as student
actor "System" as system

rectangle "Content Management System" {
  usecase "Upload Resource" as UC0501
  usecase "Validate File Type" as validate_file
  usecase "Store Metadata" as store_metadata
  usecase "Create Thumbnail" as create_thumbnail
  usecase "Manage File Metadata" as UC0502
  usecase "Version Control" as UC0503
  usecase "Archive Previous" as archive_previous
  usecase "Stream/Embed Content" as UC0504
  usecase "Delete Resource" as UC0505
  usecase "Check Dependencies" as check_dependencies
  usecase "Access Resources" as access_resources
}

' Actor Associations
instructor --> UC0501 : **Association**
instructor --> UC0505 : **Association**
student --> access_resources : **Association**
s3_system --> UC0502 : **Association**
system --> UC0503 : **Association**
system --> UC0504 : **Association**

' Use Case Relationships
UC0501 ..> validate_file : **<<include>>**
UC0501 ..> store_metadata : **<<include>>**
UC0501 ..> create_thumbnail : **<<extend>>**
UC0503 ..> archive_previous : **<<include>>**
UC0505 ..> check_dependencies : **<<include>>**

@enduml